<section class="about-hero">
    <h1>Welcome to SmartMarket</h1>
    <p>Your complete multi-vendor e-commerce platform designed for modern digital commerce.</p>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
    <h2>What is SmartMarket?</h2>
    <p>
        SmartMarket is a powerful online marketplace that connects customers, sellers, and administrators 
        in one unified platform. It enables businesses to showcase their products, manage inventory, 
        and process secure transactions while providing customers with a smooth and reliable shopping experience.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
    <h2>How SmartMarket Works</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Customers browse products, add them to their cart, and complete secure payments.</li>
        <li>Sellers manage their own stores, upload products, and track sales performance.</li>
        <li>Administrators monitor platform activity, approve products, and maintain system integrity.</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
    <h2>User Roles</h2>

    <div class="role">
        <h3>Customer</h3>
        <p>
            Customers can explore products, view detailed information, manage their shopping cart,
            place orders, and track purchases. The platform ensures a simple, fast, and secure checkout experience.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="role">
        <h3>Seller</h3>
        <p>
            Sellers can create and manage their own product listings, upload product images,
            manage stock levels, monitor sales, and grow their online business efficiently.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="role">
        <h3>Administrator</h3>
        <p>
            Administrators oversee the entire system. They approve or deactivate products,
            manage users, monitor transactions, and ensure platform quality and security.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
    <h2>Platform Features & Specifications</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Multi-vendor architecture</li>
        <li>Secure authentication and role-based access control</li>
        <li>Product approval system</li>
        <li>Shopping cart management</li>
        <li>Order tracking and sales statistics</li>
        <li>Secure online payments</li>
        <li>Cloud-based image hosting</li>
        <li>Responsive and user-friendly design</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
    <h2>Security & Reliability</h2>
    <p>
        SmartMarket implements secure user authentication, protected sessions, 
        and strict access permissions to ensure that each user only accesses 
        features appropriate to their role. All transactions are processed securely,
        and product images are stored in reliable cloud storage for high availability.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
    <h2>User Experience & Usability</h2>
    <p>
        SmartMarket is designed with usability in mind. The interface is clean,
        intuitive, and easy to navigate. Whether you are browsing products,
        managing a store, or administering the platform, the system provides
        a seamless and organized experience.
    </p>
</section>

